<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对巴斯一家人来说，这一切都发生的太快了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸在城里找到了一份很好的工作，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以他们马上就要搬回去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们第二天很早就起床了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们带着自家做的饼干，拜访了邻居们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们希望说声谢谢，也想说声再见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些饼干是为您准备的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们对詹金斯一家人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，赛伊和简拜访了基弗先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和鲍比去看了贝克尔先生和西尔弗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们很舍不得这些新朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们回到家里的时候，爸爸已经装好车了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点儿打包吧，孩子们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他叫着孩子们，“我们没有太多时间了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们盯着车旁边的一个个箱子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，潘瑟深吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还没有跟休伊说再见！”她低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们朝着树林跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要去哪里啊？”爸爸叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去跟一个朋友道别！”赛伊大声回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们并没有停下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一直跑到了休伊的井边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊赶快将木桶放了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又一次费了很大功夫才找到休伊的壳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他还是把休伊拉了上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像昨天一样，休伊看上去有点儿不同了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他甚至对着孩子们微笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是来许最后一个愿望的吗？”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最后一个愿望？你要去哪里吗？”潘瑟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为你们要走了。”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道的？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊再次微笑着说：“我们奥伦族知道我们需要知道的一切。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“休伊。”潘瑟说。她的声音开始哽咽了：“我们会想你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人也伤心地点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你实现了我们的愿望。”赛伊感激地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们很抱歉，但我们没有什么能给你的。”简哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们烤了一些饼干。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们把它们都送出去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“饼干？”休伊做了个鬼脸，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很高兴你们没有把饼干给我。我不喜欢人类的食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他更温柔地看着每个孩子：“但谢谢你们想到我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还能来看你吗？”简满怀希望地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“恐怕不行了。”休伊说着摇摇头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为，我也要离开了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“离开？”孩子们大喊，“去哪里啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去我的下一站。”休伊回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们怎么才能找到你呢？”简哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她完全不在意眼泪从脸上滚落。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊的鳍开始一开一合。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的脑袋从一边转到另一边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他的整个身体都开始发光，很亮很亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天。”他说。“你们会遇到另一口井的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们朝里看，也许我就在那里。但是，”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他继续说道，“在你们的心灵更深处去寻找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们就一定会找到我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会想你的，休伊。”孩子们流着泪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们站在那里哭着，没人说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，赛伊开口了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想我们必须得走了。”他抽着鼻子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过别忘了把我放回井里去。”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊充满爱地捧起了休伊的壳，把它轻轻地放到了木桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，赛伊，潘瑟，鲍比，还有简！”休伊挥着手说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，休伊！”孩子们大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊最后一次将木桶放回了井里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看着休伊的壳消失在了那个黑黑的洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在孩子们转身准备回家的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟说：“我还有最后一个愿望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但休伊已经走了。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系的。”她回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>349127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的愿望是什么？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>356846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望休伊一切都好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>356847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望他去任何地方都能找到快乐。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>362522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>368859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道这个愿望会成真呢？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>368860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>377499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为生命中最好的愿望就是你为他人许下的愿望。”潘瑟回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>377500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>385917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴斯家的孩子们手牵着手走出了森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>